 I joined with my friend and in game brother Aailin for his epic final stage in Plane of Fear! Dying and going LD due ISP problems I wasn’t able to log immediately. He petitioned because he knew I was having serious RL issues that might (and it turned out that it did ) prevent me from logging back for awhile. After 3 weeks things settled down in RL and I logged back to find out that I lost all my items due to corpse decay. Aailin told me that he petitioned and got the reply from a guid that everything will be ok once I came back and petitioned. I I did that everyday for a month now! Guide after Guide gave the “don’t worry about it, we are waiting for gm will look into it and we put it on the fast track panel) NOTHING happened. I never saw a GM and when I send them an email they replied with “policy number whatever blah blah …… tough luck, live with it)! <br>
I can’t believe this, shit happens and I understand but to be so inconsiderate to players is just not right. If you can’t (or won’t) do it why tell me and my friends that they will fix it. I am very disappointed with all this carp. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/azindar/sign.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
